what is good night mr tom about please london is poised on the brink of world war timid scrawny willie beech the abused child of a single mother is evacuated to the english countryside at first he is terrified of everything of the country sounds and sights even of mr tom the gruff kindly old man who has taken him in but gradually willie forgets the hate and despair of his past he learns to love a world he never knew existed a world of friendship and affection in which harsh words and daily beatings have no place then a telegram comes willie must return to his mother in london when weeks pass by with no word from willie mr tom sets out for london to look for the young boy he has come to love as a son actually i've never read this but now i'm interested Knots Landing Night (book) Miss Saigon The Marshall Mathers LP Kurt Cobain Pitaten Edward R. Murrow EastEnders Johnny Cash The Smoking Room Lili The Chronicles of Narnia Taken Death of a Salesman The Chemical Brothers Dead Like Me Tom Jones (singer) Theseus Willie Nelson Sin City Good Times The Jazz Singer Phonics Infidels The Velvet Underground Melanie Wilkes Kodocha Sant Thakar Singh I'm Sorry I Haven't a Clue Friendship The Human Stain Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Humphrey Bogart One Tree Hill (TV series) The Dalek Invasion of Earth Cromwellian conquest of Ireland Portuguese language Michel Henry Academy Award for Best Art Direction Henry V of England Neighbours New York Giants William Saroyan The Amber Spyglass William Shakespeare War of the Spanish Succession Lewis Carroll The Adventures of Jimmy Neutron: Boy Genius Church of Christ, Scientist Aramaic of Jesus The Daily Show Shaggy dog story About a Boy Nineteen Eighty-Four Elizabeth II of the United Kingdom Great Teacher Onizuka Bj__rn Borg Jan Smuts First English Civil War Leonard Cohen Feral child The Subtle Knife Bulgarian language Empire Burlesque Love You The Realm of the Elderlings/Characters James Dobson Socrates The Grim Adventures of Billy and Mandy Recur